import numpy as np
def Method2(a, b):
    group1, group2= np.meshgrid([*a],[*b])
    print(group1)
    print(group2)
    print(type(group1))
    print(dir(group1))
    return group1 == group2
v=Method2("group","groupChar")
print(type(v))
